############################################################

lifeStage ‚äë attribute
‚àÉlifeStage.‚ä§ ‚äë Animal
‚ä§ ‚äë ‚àÄlifeStage.{"Juvenile","Subadult","Adult","Unknown"}
‚â§1 lifeStage.‚ä§
@db lifeStage "life_stage"
@label lifeStage "Life Stage"
