habitatQuality ‚äë attribute
‚àÉhabitatQuality.‚ä§ ‚äë Habitat
‚ä§ ‚äë ‚àÄhabitatQuality.xsd:decimal[‚â•1 ‚äì ‚â§5]
‚â§1 habitatQuality.‚ä§
@db habitatQuality "habitat_quality"
