studiesStatement ‚äë ‚àÉstatementRelationship.{studies}

confidenceLevel ‚äë attribute
‚àÉconfidenceLevel.‚ä§ ‚äë studiesStatement
‚ä§ ‚äë ‚àÄconfidenceLevel.{"Low","Medium","High"}
‚â§1 confidenceLevel.‚ä§
@db confidenceLevel "confidence_level"
