observationMethod ‚äë attribute
‚àÉobservationMethod.‚ä§ ‚äë recordsAnimalStatement
‚ä§ ‚äë ‚àÄobservationMethod.{"Camera Trap","Direct Sight","Track","Audio"}
‚â§1 observationMethod.‚ä§
@db observationMethod "observation_method"
